summary: This mod allows all kinds of mischievous folk to bypass the presence of guards. This mod is Role-Play orientated and will continue to remain so. I hope you like it.
descriptionHtml:
It has recently come to my attention that there are several addons that do something similar to this add-on. I would like to say that those addons are complete, mine is no where near complete. 

When this addon is done, it will have fully fledged tunnels into the cities, with several ways to access key buildings and structures for some general sneaking around. This allows all kinds of mischievous folk to bypass the presence of guards. This mod is Role-Play orientated and will continue to remain so.

If you wish to use BETA version of this addon (which will always contain more content) please use the version on the Skyrim Workshop found here: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=95754858
author: Imoja
